definitions.definition: The time after the sun has set but when the sky is still lit by sunlight; the evening twilight period.
examples: Witnessing the dusk gives a feeling of solace .
We caught a beautiful view of the dusk.

definitions.definition: The condition of being dusky ; duskiness
